_:N15bafad45c9041518d9a93b4ec50c046 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Visit the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/about/procurement\" class=\"govuk-link\">MoJ procurement</a> pages for further information.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"becoming-a-supplier\">Becoming a supplier</h2>\n\n<p>GFSL draws on a diverse supply chain for goods and corporate services.</p>\n\n<p>We encourage interested organisations to make contact and enquire about working with us at  <a href=\"mailto:gfsl_supplychain@govfsl.com\" class=\"govuk-link\">gfsl_supplychain@govfsl.com</a>.</p>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
